OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK government to be        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Freported to UN over strike 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Flaw                        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Trades Union Congress (TUC) says it
OL,6, is reporting the UK government to the  
OL,7, United Nations watchdog on workers'    
OL,8, rights over a new strikes law.         
OL,10,FNew rules on strikes will require some 
OL,11,Femployees to work during industrial    
OL,12,Faction - or face being sacked.         
OL,14,FThe TUC said the legislation fell short
OL,15,Fof international legal standards.      
OL,17,FThe government said the new rules      
OL,18,F"protect the lives and livelihoods of  
OL,19,Fthe general public" as well as access  
OL,20,Fto public services.                    
